 the same as I do. This has been quite an ordeal. I thought they would never let me go — and those allusions to strangling and drowning were a bit tactless. Nice boys, I admit, hearts of gold, but uncivilized — their only defect really. Otherwise, I agree with you, they are grand. While I was standing —'

This is the fourth lamp-post, and one tenth of the bridge. Few of them are alight.

